<p>From <a href="http://www.nivi.com/blog/article/time-to-hit-the-reset-button/">Nivi : Time to Hit the Reset Button on the Media Industry</a>.:</p>
<p><b>QUOTE</b></p>
<blockquote><p>When the people revolt, there are not enough police to maintain the old order. You need a new Constitution. Content owners: publish complete libraries online using open protocols like BitTorrent and a published API. And find a way for people to pay you when they get the content. Let the hackers and entrepreneurs create the iTunes-for-video that accesses and organizes your content.</p>

<p>Time to hit the reset button on the media industry.
</p>
<p>Here endeth the lesson.</p></blockquote>
